1, Please download the HelloFlask folder, config.py, HelloFlask.py, requirments.txt and runserver.py from the master branch or jiqi_wang branch

2, Check the requirment.txt and download necessary modules if needed.

3, If the database doesn't work (What you enter in the web app doesn't show up):
    a, Open terminal and goes to the file location
    b, Type flask db init
    c, Type flask db migrate -m "comment"
    d, Type flask upgrade
